        },
        {
          category: 'Business',
          items: ['Entrepreneurship', 'Team Leadership', 'Strategic Planning', 'Market Analysis']
        }
      ],
      achievements: [
        'Successfully launched first children\'s book series',
        'Established partnerships with educational institutions',
        'Created engaging content for young readers',
        'Developed innovative storytelling techniques'
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    id: 'artist',
    title: 'Artist',
    icon: 'fa-palette',
    content: `Rashmi's artistic journey brings a unique visual perspective to her books. Her illustrations blend traditional Indian art elements with modern design, creating a distinctive style that appeals to both children and adults.`,
    instagram: {
      username: 'mightyloka',
      feed: [
        {
          image: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/media/?size=l',
          link: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/',
          caption: 'Latest artwork from our children\'s book series'
        },
        {
          image: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/media/?size=l',
          link: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/',
          caption: 'Traditional Indian art meets modern storytelling'
        },
        {
          image: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/media/?size=l',
          link: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/',
          caption: 'Behind the scenes of our illustration process'
        },
        {
          image: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/media/?size=l',
          link: 'https://www.instagram.com/p/C4X2YQNvJKL/',
          caption: 'Character sketches and development'
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    id: 'mother',
    title: 'Mother',
    icon: 'fa-heart',
    content: `As a mom to a curious 6-year-old daughter, Rashmi noticed her little one's endless questions about Indian festivals, each one a bridge to their roots. It hit her then: our kids shouldn't just hear tales, they should dance with the gods, soar with the heroes, and carry them like treasures. Her daughter's awe for Hanuman, her caped crusader, birthed Chotu and Chutki - spirited characters blending mythic valor with modern flair.`
